  "data": {
    "title": "Salesmsg: Business Texting & Calling Made Simple",
    "excerpt": "Discover Salesmsg, the SMS and calling platform that helps businesses automate follow-ups and close more deals. See how it works.",
    "featured_image": {
      "$media": {
        "url": "https://tonyciencia.com/blog/what-is-salesmsg.jpg",
        "alt": "Salesmsg: Business Texting & Calling Made Simple",
        "filename": "what-is-salesmsg.jpg"
      }
    },
    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You already know that email open rates are tanking. Most cold emails sit unread, buried under a pile of newsletters nobody asked for. Meanwhile, SMS messages get a 98% open rate — and most people read them within three minutes.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "That gap between \"sent\" and \"seen\" is exactly what Salesmsg was built to close.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you run a sales team, a small business, or a growing agency, you've probably struggled with the same problem: your leads ignore your emails, your reps waste hours dialing voicemail boxes, and follow-ups fall through the cracks. Salesmsg fixes all of that with a single platform for two-way texting, bulk SMS, calling, and automated sequences — all from one clean dashboard.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://join.salesmessage.com/1kyh4nmhxj5g"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've tested dozens of communication tools over the past few years. Some are great at email, some handle calls well, and a few do okay with SMS. Salesmsg is the first one I've seen that actually nails all three without forcing you to stitch together five different apps. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You can try Salesmsg here",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and see what I mean.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let me walk you through what it does, who it's for, and why it's become one of my go-to recommendations.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What Is Salesmsg?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Salesmsg is a business SMS and calling platform designed for teams that need to communicate with leads, customers, and contacts at scale. It's not a consumer messaging app repackaged for businesses — it was purpose-built from day one for sales, marketing, and customer success teams.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "At its core, Salesmsg lets you:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Send and receive text messages (both 1-on-1 and bulk)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Make and receive phone calls from the same interface",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Automate follow-up sequences based on triggers and behavior",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Manage all conversations in a shared inbox your whole team can access",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Integrate with your existing CRM, helpdesk, and marketing stack",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform runs on actual local phone numbers — not short codes or shared pool numbers. That means your texts look like they come from a real person, which is why response rates tend to be significantly higher than email or generic SMS blasts.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Think of it as the texting equivalent of having a dedicated sales line, but with automation superpowers bolted on.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How Salesmsg Works: A Quick Walkthrough",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Getting started with Salesmsg takes about ten minutes. You sign up, pick a local phone number (or port your existing one), and you're ready to send your first text.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's the typical workflow:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. Import Your Contacts",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Upload a CSV, connect your CRM, or add contacts manually. Salesmsg supports tags and custom fields, so you can segment your audience however you like.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. Compose Your Message",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Write a text, add merge fields (first name, company, etc.), and attach media if needed. You can send one-off messages or create bulk campaigns to hundreds or thousands of contacts.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. Set Up Automations",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is where Salesmsg really shines. You can build sequences that automatically send follow-up texts based on replies, time delays, or CRM triggers. If a lead doesn't respond to your first message, Salesmsg can send a nudge two days later — without anyone lifting a finger.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. Handle Replies in the Shared Inbox",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "When someone texts back, the conversation pops into your team's shared inbox. Any rep can pick it up, and the full message history stays visible. No more \"who was talking to this lead?\" confusion.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "5. Make Calls When It Makes Sense",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If a text conversation gets hot, you can call the lead directly from Salesmsg — no need to switch apps. The platform logs call activity alongside text history, so you get a complete picture of every interaction.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-salesmsg"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you want a detailed walkthrough, check out our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "step-by-step guide on how to use Salesmsg",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". It covers everything from account setup to advanced automation recipes.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Key Features & What's New",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Salesmsg ships updates regularly, and they've added some genuinely useful features recently. Here's what stands out:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Two-Way Texting at Scale",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Most SMS tools let you blast messages out. Salesmsg lets you have actual conversations. Every text is a thread, and your team can manage thousands of threads simultaneously without losing context.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "SMS Marketing Campaigns",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Need to send a promotion to 5,000 contacts? Salesmsg handles bulk campaigns with built-in compliance (opt-out handling, quiet hours, TCPA compliance). You schedule campaigns, track delivery rates, and measure responses — all in one place.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI-Powered Replies",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Salesmsg now includes AI assistance that can suggest responses based on conversation context. It's not replacing your reps — it's helping them reply faster and more consistently. For high-volume teams, this alone can save hours each week.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Automated Follow-Up Sequences",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Set up multi-step sequences that trigger based on behavior. If a lead opens but doesn't reply, send a follow-up. If they reply with a question, route it to the right rep. The automation builder is visual and straightforward — no engineering degree required.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Calling Integration",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Make and receive calls directly from the Salesmsg interface. Call recordings, logs, and notes stay tied to the contact's profile. It's especially handy for sales teams that want to text first and call when interest is confirmed.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CRM & Tool Integrations",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Salesmsg plugs into HubSpot, Salesforce, Pipedrive, Zapier, and dozens of other tools. You can sync contact data, trigger automations from CRM events, and log every interaction back to your pipeline automatically.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/salesmsg-new-features"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Want the full breakdown? Our article on ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Salesmsg's newest features and updates",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " dives deeper into each release.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/why-choose-salesmsg"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you're comparing Salesmsg against other automation tools and wondering how it stacks up, we also wrote a piece on ",
