        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Who Is Salesmsg Ideal For?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Salesmsg isn't trying to be everything to everyone. It's built for specific use cases, and it handles those incredibly well. Here's who gets the most value out of it:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Sales Teams (SMBs and Mid-Market)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If your reps are cold-calling and emailing but getting ghosted, adding SMS changes the game. Texts feel personal, they get read, and they spark conversations that email never will. Sales teams using Salesmsg typically see response rates 3–5x higher than email-only outreach.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Real Estate Agents & Brokers",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Real estate is a speed game. When a lead fills out a form, the agent who texts first wins the deal. Salesmsg lets agents respond instantly — even with automated first-touch messages — and manage dozens of active conversations from their phone or laptop.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Agencies Running Client Campaigns",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Marketing agencies use Salesmsg to manage SMS campaigns for multiple clients from a single dashboard. Each client gets their own phone number, their own automations, and their own reporting. It's clean, scalable, and way easier than juggling separate tools.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Customer Success & Support Teams",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Not every customer wants to call a hotline or wait for an email reply. Salesmsg gives support teams a direct line — literally. Customers text in with questions, and your team responds from the shared inbox. It feels personal and fast, which drives satisfaction scores up.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "E-commerce & DTC Brands",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Appointment reminders, order updates, abandoned cart nudges, flash sale alerts — all of these work better via SMS than email. E-commerce brands use Salesmsg to drive repeat purchases and reduce no-shows.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
